{"tid":2408360,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黑白照公布喜訊　哈利梅根迎第二胎","createTime":"2021-02-15T00:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T07:04:35.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"0545372bf437ec45d44524bec60c955515d8c247","tid":2408360,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T00:36:33.000Z","msg":"英國哈利王子和夫人梅根周日（2/14）宣布梅根懷第2胎，並公開一張兩人在樹蔭下，梅根躺在哈利膝上並撫著隆起的肚子的黑白照片。<br />\n<br />\n哈利和梅根的發言人表示，「我們可以證實亞契即將成為哥哥。薩賽克斯公爵及夫人很高興將迎接他們的第2個孩子。」<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》（DailyMail）記者引述白金漢宮消息報導，女王伊莉莎白二世、查爾斯王儲和威廉王子提前接獲通知，整個王室都「很開心」，並祝福哈利和梅根一切順利。<br />\n<br />\n這個即將出世的寶寶會是英國王位第8順位繼承人。哈利和梅根在去年1月宣布脫離王室，不再執行王室成員職責並放棄使用「殿下」（HRH）的王室名銜，也不再接受王室撥款。兩人目前定居美國加州洛杉磯。（盧宥竹／綜合外電報導）<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210215/XA6QQHHIZ5ET3KTADRHOLMF5NI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210215%2FXA6QQHHIZ5ET3KTADRHOLMF5NI%2F&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4edDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=dc5e236d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210215%2FXA6QQHHIZ5ET3KTADRHOLMF5NI%2F&h=15d9b27f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210215/XA6QQHHIZ5ET3KTADRHOLMF5NI/</a>"},{"pid":"89c54db75c0c27cc296463582b06fc19a57103f3","tid":2408360,"uid":255980,"like":28,"dislike":6,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T00:37:15.000Z","msg":"又多隻Nigger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5261238b34eef930b0a55061fa74662fef97945e","tid":2408360,"uid":125357,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T00:40:40.000Z","msg":"雜種"},{"pid":"c9cffe00d491030119cce67017035dab7de72662","tid":2408360,"uid":78349,"like":68,"dislike":0,"score":68,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T00:41:50.000Z","msg":"離開皇室仲叫乜公爵夫人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e66639